Description: You only get one set of teeth, so you should take the best possible care of them. The Dazzlepro elements sonic toothbrush and UV sanitizing base uses sonic technology and four brush modes to clean and whiten you smile, encourage healthy gums, and remove surface stains. Choose from: “clean” for a thorough, deep clean; “soft” for an extra-gentle brushing; “whiten” for polishing away surface stains; and “massage” to stimulate gums, which can help reduce tartar buildup that can lead to gum disease. The Dazzlepro elements sonic toothbrush and UV sanitizing base brushes your teeth using 40,000 tiny strokes per minute, compared to just 300 strokes per minute (on average) you are able to do with a manual toothbrush. It also has an auto-shut off function after you’ve brushed for the American dental association-recommended two minutes, so you don’t even have to think about it. What’S more, a 30-second interval timer reminds you to move from one section of your mouth to the next so that all of your teeth get cleaned evenly and thoroughly.
